branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
HRZ recirculating chillers are especially suited for high technology sectors, by conforming to several SEMI equipment standards and regulating fluid temperature &#xb1;0.1&#xb0;C. This model includes an energy-saving inverter compressor and inverter pump, achieving lower power consumption and requiring a lower average flow rate of facility water for refrigerant heat extraction. 10 kW of cooling capacity is available at 20&#xb0;C coolant set point. Multiple coolant types can be selected for this model.
&lt;/p&gt;

